Date: Wed, 1 Dec 2021 10:54:53 -0800
Subject: Bluetooth: HCI: Use skb_pull_data to parse BR/EDR events
Patch-mainline: v5.17-rc1
Git-commit: ae61a10d9d46c4a0844c46d0863bf991c4dda66c
